g.text: Reciprocity Monitoring

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Notice Micro Signals

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: tone, body language, response latency. Does this person make eye contact? Do they lean in or pull back? How quickly do they

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: respond to messages? These aren't definitive tells, but they're data points.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Identify whether person is responsive, neutral or avoidant

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Responsive people engage, ask follow-up euqestions, and initiate contact. Neutral people respond when prompted but don't

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: escalate. Avoid people delay, deflect or disappear.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Avoid labelling, infer tendencies

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Don't conclude "this person is insecure" or "this person has trust issues." Instead, notice patterns: "This person seems to

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: warm up slowly" or "This person prefer clear structure before opening up"

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Ask disarming questions

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: "What am I missing?" is my go-to. It's simple, non-threatening, and invites collaboration rather than

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: defensiveness.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Pause before responding; 3-7 seconds is normal

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: This feels absurdly long at first, but it gives room to think, signals composure and prevents reactive

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: performance

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Match energy; avoid over-injecting humour or personal disclosure too early

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: If someone is reserved. don't flood them with energy. If someone is expressive, don't hold back to the

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: point of seeming disinterested. Calibration is everything.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Track responses to invitations or follow-ups

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Did they accept? Decline with an alternative? Ignore? Each response is data.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Note repeated non-reciprocation; consider holding neutral or

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: stopping investment

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: If you've reached out two or three times without a reciprocal invitation, that's a pattern.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: It doesn't mean th person is bad or that you're unworthy. It means the relationship isn't

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: balanced, and further investment may drain you.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Match energy; avoid over-injecting humour or personal disclosure

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: too early

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Are you the one always initiating? Always remembering? Always accommodating? If the

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: effort is consistently one-sided, the relationship may offer belonging but not closeness.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Boundaries and Hard No(s)

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Clearly define your emotional bandwidth: how much time and energy you'll

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: invest. This isn't cold or transactional, its protective. You can't pour from

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: an empty cup. Fill your cup first.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: 1. Ignoring repeating invitations from non-reciprocating contacts

g.text: Hard No Examples

g.text: 2. Refusing unsolicited advice that assumes your constraints don't exist

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: 3. Declining high-pressure social situations that drain rather than energize

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: 4. Stopping hope-driven escalation after repeated attempts caused stress

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: or self-criticism

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Family adapation: accept stable relationships without depth. Limit

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: emotionally draining interactions. It's ok to maintain distance while

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: preserving the relationship

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Hope vs. emotional costs

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Evaluate: Is this initiation hope-driven and manageable?

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Hope is not inherently bad. It's the engine of connection. But if hope

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: becomes a burden i.e., if every unanswered message spirals into self-

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: criticism, then the cost is too high.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: If repeated attempts cause stress or self-criticism, pause or stop. This

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: isn't defeat. It's discernment. Some relationships aren't worth the

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: emotional cost, and recognizing that is growth

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Document progress and small wins to reinforce positive social learning.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Did someone remember somethign you mentioned? Did they follow up?

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Did they show effort? Notice these moments. They're evidence that

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: connection is possible, that your temperament isn't a barrier, and that

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: the right people will meet you where you are.
